STATE
v.
Teddy L. BOLES, Sr. No. 426P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 24, 2008. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Tom Horner, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 27th day of August 2007 by Defendant for "Petition for Discretionary Review":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 24th day of January 2008."
